  <brief_title>An Open Study to Investigate the Safety and Efficacy of Optivate® in Haemophilia A Patients Undergoing Surgery.</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Study to Investigate the Safety and Efficacy of Optivate® in Haemophilia A Patients Undergoing Surgery.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Bio Products Laboratory</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Bio Products Laboratory</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of the study is to investigate the safety and efficacy of Optivate®,
      administered in appropriate dosage to present bleeding and achieve haemostasis in patients
      with Haemophilia A undergoing surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
